Sentencas: The Artificial Neural Network (ANN) can be applied to simulate an object's behaviour without an algorithmic solution merely by utilizing available experimental data.
Titulo: Modelling the SOFC behaviours by artificial neural network

Sentencas: The ANN is used for modelling singular cell behaviour.
Titulo: Modelling the SOFC behaviours by artificial neural network

Sentencas: The optimal network architecture is shown and commented.
Titulo: Modelling the SOFC behaviours by artificial neural network

Sentencas: The error backpropagation algorithm was used for an ANN training procedure.
Titulo: Modelling the SOFC behaviours by artificial neural network

Sentencas: The ANN based SOFC model has the following input parameters: current density, temperature, fuel volume flow density (ml min(-1) cm(-2)), and oxidant volume flow density.
Titulo: Modelling the SOFC behaviours by artificial neural network

Sentencas: Based on these input parameters, cell voltage is predicted by the model.
Titulo: Modelling the SOFC behaviours by artificial neural network

Sentencas: Obtained results show that the ANN can be successfully used for modelling the singular solid oxide fuel cell.
Titulo: Modelling the SOFC behaviours by artificial neural network

Sentencas: The self-learning process of the ANN provides an opportunity to adapt the model to new situations (e.g. certain types of impurities at inlet streams etc.).
Titulo: Modelling the SOFC behaviours by artificial neural network

Sentencas: Based on the results from this study it can be concluded that, by using the ANN, an SOFC can be modelled with relatively high accuracy.
Titulo: Modelling the SOFC behaviours by artificial neural network

Sentencas: In contrast to traditional models, the ANN is able to predict cell voltage without knowledge of numerous physical, chemical, and electrochemical factors.
Titulo: Modelling the SOFC behaviours by artificial neural network
